oracle.mapviewer.share
Class ThemeStyleInfo

java.lang.Object
  oracle.mapviewer.share.ThemeStyleInfo

public class ThemeStyleInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This bean class describes how a style is used in the context of a theme. It provides such information as the name of the style, whether it is used as a rendering or labeling style, whether it's for highlighting only, and if it is an advanced style. This class is typically used for the purpose of creating a nice looking map legend.
